description: Adam Heppinstall KC, who was charged with ruling whether the selection of Richard Sharp (pictured) was above board, re-posted comments.

title: Tropical Cyclone Gabrielle draws closer to Norfolk Island with warning of gale-force winds
description: The category three cyclone is rapidly moving towards the tourist hot spot and is expected to pass through Norfolk Island on Saturday evening.

title: PETER TATCHELL reveals his secret love with footballer Justin Fashanu that sustained him
description: PETER TATCHELL: As I was cycling along a quiet road, the sound of a vehicle close behind alerted me to danger.

title: EDEN CONFIDENTIAL: Surprise for Lord Snowdon's secret daughter Polly as she finds 'Mr Darcy'
description: RICHARD EDEN: Every family has its secrets. Few, though, can match the disorientating truth which remained unknown to Polly Fry until she was 45.

title: Detective who downloaded child abuse images from his police force's files is jailed for four years
description: Detective Constable James Jordan accessed Cambridgeshire Police's confidential systems to view child abuse videos and pictures of female victims in voyeurism cases.

title: Boris Johnson might not appear before MPs investigating him over Partygate until after Easter
description: The former prime minister has still not been contacted by the Commons privileges committee - even though it began its inquiry more than nine months ago.

title: Christians are put at a disadvantage in public life as their faith is unfashionable, claims Tory MP
description: Danny Kruger said it is damaging to society that the religion of contemporary culture is 'liberal individualism', which values the freedom to do as one pleases above all else.

title: Californians fleeing the Golden State for tax breaks and other amenities in Nevada
description: Thousands of Californians leaving the Golden State looking to escape the rampant homelessness and high cost of living are landing in neighboring Nevada, overrunning the state's few major cities.

title: Superintendent who smeared girl who killed herself after being beaten by bullies seen outside school
description: Residents in New Jersey came together to mourn the loss of Adriana Kuch, 14, who was beaten in the halls of her school and took her own life. She died two days after a video came out.

title: HMS Queen Elizabeth sends Chinese sub packing on her maiden patrol
description: HMS Queen Elizabeth was shadowed by a Russian-built Kilo class Chinese submarine during her first operational tour of the Far East in Summer 2021. The tense action was captured by a documentary crew.

title: Mormon Church faces SEC probe over past efforts to keep $100 billion investments a secret
description: The Mormon Church's financial management arm is under investigation by the Securities and Exchange Commission over  efforts to keep its billion dollar investment fund a secret.

title: Girl, 14, slashed with a knife outside school as 18-year-old boy is arrested
description: Police have opened an investigation after a 14-year-old pupil was attacked with a knife shortly before 3.30pm today at Ernesford Grange Community Academy in Coventry.
